premium/first-conscientious-objector-of-the-gaza-war-freed-after-more-than-six-months-in-prison/00000190-a301-da1a-adf0-a79de1290000</guid></item><item><title>贝埃里 10 月 7 日调查揭示的以色列军队的失败只是问题的一部分</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-armys-failure-revealed-in-beeri-oct-7-probe-is-only-part-of-the-picture/00000190-a2e9-d962-a3b7-b2ff646f0000</link><description>调查结果的很大一部分是优先顺序有缺陷、指挥官犯下的错误以及军队采取行动所花费的大量时间。但这不应转移人们对政治层面失败的注意力</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 18:41:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-armys-failure-revealed-in-beeri-oct-7-probe-is-only-part-of-the-picture/00000190-a2e9-d962-a3b7-b2ff646f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 279 天：以色列国防部长呼吁调查哈马斯获得权力的条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-279-defense-minister-calls-to-probe-conditions-that-empowered-hamas/00000190-a2bc-ddf1-abb6-effd7f930001</link><description>以色列人在以色列北部真主党无人机袭击中身受重伤 ■ 辛贝特酋长率领的以色列代表团前往开罗继续停战谈判 ■ 以色列国防军公布 10 月 7 日贝埃里基布兹事件的调查结果 ■ 以色列国防部长呼吁建立国家调查委员会“在过去十年中导致哈马斯权力建立的条件” ■ 战争开始 279 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 17:07:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-279-defense-minister-calls-to-probe-conditions-that-empowered-hamas/00000190-a2bc-ddf1-abb6-effd7f930001</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府采取重大举措，寻求对土耳其进口商品实施贸易禁运</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/in-a-drastic-step-israeli-government-seeks-trade-embargo-on-imports-from-turkey/00000190-a1b0-dbad-adfc-f5b907e50000</link><description>总理办公室发布了一项史无前例的提案，全面禁止从土耳其直接进口以色列。以色列商会联合会主席认为此举是以色列战争的另一条战线的开辟，这是以色列消费者无法承受的</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 17:04:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/in-a-drastic-step-israeli-government-seeks-trade-embargo-on-imports-from-turkey/00000190-a1b0-dbad-adfc-f5b907e50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称其在 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击中“未能保护”贝埃里基布兹居民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-it-failed-to-protect-kibbutz-beeri-residents-in-oct-7-hamas-attack/00000190-a213-dd20-abfa-fe1748d00000</link><description>以色列国防军官方调查发现，部队对数千名恐怖分子大规模袭击的情况毫无准备。 ■ 缺乏协调，导致部队在没有与哈马斯接触的情况下聚集在基布兹入口处。 ■ 决定向扣押以色列人质的基布兹家发射坦克炮弹，这一决定是“专业和负责任的”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 16:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-it-failed-to-protect-kibbutz-beeri-residents-in-oct-7-hamas-attack/00000190-a213-dd20-abfa-fe1748d00000</guid></item><item><title>美国对犹太至上主义组织 Lehava 和约旦河西岸前哨基地实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-places-sanctions-on-jewish-supremacist-organization-lehava-west-bank-outposts/00000190-a242-dbad-adfc-f6db37a20000</link><description>其中两名受制裁人员与 Tzav 9 有联系，该组织阻止向加沙提供人道主义援助。 Lehava组织也在受制裁之列，该组织回应称：“美国年老且反犹太主义的总统并没有吓到我们”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 15:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-places-sanctions-on-jewish-supremacist-organization-lehava-west-bank-outposts/00000190-a242-dbad-adfc-f6db37a20000</guid></item><item><title>在耶路撒冷最动荡的地点之一举办艺术节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-07-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/staging-an-art-festival-at-one-of-jerusalems-most-volatile-sites/00000190-a20f-d03e-a5fd-bbbfee850000</link><description>锡安山是今年马诺芬节的举办地，两个节庆地点都有与剥夺、入侵和有争议的圣地有关的展品</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 14:29:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-07-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/staging-an-art-festival-at-one-of-jerusalems-most-volatile-sites/00000190-a20f-d03e-a5fd-bbbfee850000</guid></item><item><title>“我们失败了”：以色列军队向贝埃里基布兹居民展示 10 月 7 日的调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/kibbutz-beeri-residents-say-critical-questions-remain-unanswered-after-oct-7-army-probe/00000190-a214-dd20-abfa-fe1732640000</link><description>居民们表示，“可以说调查很彻底”，但补充说，关键问题没有得到解答。他们现在呼吁成立一个国家调查委员会，“不遗余力”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 14:14:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/kibbutz-beeri-residents-say-critical-questions-remain-unanswered-after-oct-7-army-probe/00000190-a214-dd20-abfa-fe1732640000</guid></item><item><title>难怪以色列右翼认为左翼想要杀死内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-no-wonder-the-israeli-right-thinks-the-left-wants-to-kill-netanyahu/00000190-a147-dd20-abfa-ff57efa70000</link><description>右翼担心左翼分子可能会刺杀首相，只不过是那些除了暴力之外不接受任何解决方案的人的典型预测。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 12:29:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-no-wonder-the-israeli-right-thinks-the-left-wants-to-kill-netanyahu/00000190-a147-dd20-abfa-ff57efa70000</guid></item><item><title>为了达成人质协议，以色列必须解决其对拉法和埃及-加沙边境的控制问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/to-reach-a-hostage-deal-israel-must-address-its-control-of-rafah-and-egypt-gaza-border/00000190-a109-ddf1-abb6-edc90af90000</link><description>埃及要求以色列从加沙边境撤军，并要求巴勒斯坦权力机构管理加沙的过境点，而以色列则要求确保国际部队能够在脆弱的人质谈判中监督加沙-埃及边境</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/to-reach-a-hostage-deal-israel-must-address-its-control-of-rafah-and-egypt-gaza-border/00000190-a109-ddf1-abb6-edc90af90000</guid></item><item><title>获救的以色列人质起诉在加沙雇佣巴勒斯坦人质的美国非营利组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-sues-u-s-non-profit-that-employed-palestinian-captor-in-gaza/00000190-9c81-d07e-a798-beb136350000</link><description>该诉讼称，该组织的领导人“故意并故意获取和传播哈马斯的宣传”，并“物质上支持”哈马斯的恐怖主义行为</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:15:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-sues-u-s-non-profit-that-employed-palestinian-captor-in-gaza/00000190-9c81-d07e-a798-beb136350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列计划征召的极端正统人士远远不能满足军队当前的需求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-planned-draft-of-ultra-orthodox-falls-far-short-of-the-armys-current-needs/00000190-9e56-d41c-abfc-def65b770000</link><description>根据正在制定的计划，两年内将招募约 9,600 名年轻的正统派男子——远少于 63,000 名处于征兵年龄的极端正统男子。只要加沙战争持续下去，总参谋部将继续依靠预备役军人，而且在未来几年边境预计紧张的时期也是如此</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 03:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-planned-draft-of-ultra-orthodox-falls-far-short-of-the-armys-current-needs/00000190-9e56-d41c-abfc-def65b770000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，随着卡塔尔休战谈判即将恢复，哈马斯可能在“几天内”达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-hamas-deal-possible-within-days-as-qatar-truce-talks-set-to-resume/00000190-9ef8-dfb2-a799-befd66de0000</link><description>国防部长约夫·加兰特：“现在实现我们的道德义务并将人质带回家的机会有限”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 03:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-hamas-deal-possible-within-days-as-qatar-truce-talks-set-to-resume/00000190-9ef8-dfb2-a799-befd66de0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长加兰特呼吁 10 月 7 日启动国家调查：“检查我，检查总理”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article-live/u-s-cautiously-optimistic-about-gaza-cease-fire-as-sides-head-to-qatar-for-talks/00000190-9fa1-dfb2-a799-bff5e84c0000</link><description>美国对被指控破坏约旦河西岸稳定的以色列个人和实体实施制裁，尤其是勒哈瓦组织 ■ 内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，辛贝特酋长率领的代表团将前往开罗继续谈判 ■ 哈马斯声称以色列继续“拖延”以赢得时间挫败当前的停火谈判 ■ 巴勒斯坦红新月会：青少年在约旦河西岸被以色列国防军杀害</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article-live/u-s-cautiously-optimistic-about-gaza-cease-fire-as-sides-head-to-qatar-for-talks/00000190-9fa1-dfb2-a799-bff5e84c0000</guid></item><item><title>极端正统派拉比领袖指示学生无视以色列军队征召令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/leading-ultra-orthodox-rabbi-instructs-students-to-ignore-israeli-army-call-up-orders/00000190-9f8d-d962-a3b7-9fbf3f350001</link><description>以色列立陶宛极端正统派领袖拉比多夫·兰多 (Rabbi Dov Lando) 写道，“法院已向托拉世界宣战”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:15:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/leading-ultra-orthodox-rabbi-instructs-students-to-ignore-israeli-army-call-up-orders/00000190-9f8d-d962-a3b7-9fbf3f350001</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方知道在准备极端正统征兵时必须谨慎行事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-knows-it-must-tread-carefully-as-it-prepares-for-the-ultra-orthodox-draft/00000190-9dfb-dbad-adfc-fdfbbc8e0000</link><description>以色列国防军计划征召在职和退学的犹太学院学生，并打算赋予拉比对新兵服役的监督权</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 23:25:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-knows-it-must-tread-carefully-as-it-prepares-for-the-ultra-orthodox-draft/00000190-9dfb-dbad-adfc-fdfbbc8e0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：内塔尼亚胡办公室试图更改以色列内阁战时会议纪要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/report-netanyahus-bureau-tried-to-alter-minutes-of-war-time-meetings-of-israeli-cabinet/00000190-9ea1-dfb2-a799-bef5354e0000</link><description>总理的前军事秘书几个月前联系了司法部长，敲响了警钟； PMO：报告完全是谎言</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 22:06:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-11/ty-article/report-netanyahus-bureau-tried-to-alter-minutes-of-war-time-meetings-of-israeli-cabinet/00000190-9ea1-dfb2-a799-bef5354e0000</guid></item><item><title>“严厉和麦卡锡主义”：以色列议会提出法案，解雇那些被政府视为“支持恐怖”观点的学者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/knesset-advances-bill-to-fire-academics-for-views-seen-as-supporting-terror-by-govt/00000190-9e04-d03e-a5fd-9fb6744f0000</link><description>该提案允许由教育部长担任主席的高等教育委员会要求解雇，但不支付遣散费。大学校长谴责这一“麦卡锡主义”措施，警告称这可能会煽动针对教师的运动，并可能导致针对教师的暴力行为</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 20:27:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-10/ty-article/.premium/knesset-advances-bill-to-fire-academics-for-views-seen-as-supporting-terror-by-govt/00000190-9e04-d03e-a5fd-9fb6744f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>